    "body": "This may actually not be a bug with l2geth but perhaps an upstream bug with Geth. Since this is a simple transfer, the 21000 gas is taken out of the gas supply at the very beginning of execution (in the pre-checks), before tracing happens. And since this is a top-level call, there's no additional gas charged. So it looks like gas used was 0 and gas left is also 0. ",
